Byte-by-byte Description of file: table2.dat
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
   Bytes Format Units   Label    Explanations
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
   1-  7  I7    ---    [SIG2010] RR Lyrae identification number
   9- 10  A2    ---     Type     [abc ] RR Lyrae type
  12- 25 F14.12 d       Per      Period
  27- 40 F14.12 mag     uAmp     Best-fit template u band amplitude
  42- 56 F15.12 mag     umag1    Best-fit template u band maximum brightness (1)
  58- 75 F18.12 d       T0.u     Best-fit template u band epoch of maximum
                                 brightness (MJD)
  77- 79  I3    ---     Tu       Best-fit template u band ID number
  81- 94 F14.12 mag     gAmp     Best-fit template g band amplitude
  96-110 F15.12 mag     gmag1    Best-fit template g band maximum brightness (1)
 112-129 F18.12 d       T0.g     Best-fit template g band epoch of maximum
                                 brightness (MJD)
